---
// src/pages/enterprise/index.astro
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Enterprise — Specialized Repair & Fabrication"
  description="Streich Force Enterprise: specialized commercial repair and custom fabrication for retail chains, pharmacies, and commercial properties. The call you make when no one else can solve it."
  division="enterprise"
>
  <Nav active="enterprise" />

  <section class="division-hero">
    <div class="hero-grid-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Division 03 &mdash; Specialized Repair &amp; Fabrication</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Streich Force<br/><span class="accent">Enterprise</span></h1>
      <div class="hero-rule"></div>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        When no one else can figure it out — this is the call you make. Specialized repair and custom fabrication for commercial and retail properties that demand precision.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="mailto:enterprise@streichforce.com" class="btn-primary">Get In Touch</a>
        <a href="/#divisions" class="btn-ghost">All Divisions</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INTRO STATEMENT -->
  <section class="statement-section">
    <div class="statement-inner reveal">
      <blockquote>
        "If your standard contractors have tried and failed — or if you need something built that doesn't exist yet — that's exactly where we start."
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="section-label">What We Do</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Repair. Restore. Fabricate.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid reveal">
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-num">01</div>
        <h3>Specialized Commercial Repair</h3>
        <p>Service and repair work for commercial retail chains that requires a higher level of technical expertise than standard maintenance contractors can provide. Called in when others have been unable to complete the job.</p>
        <div class="service-clients">
          <p class="clients-label">Clients include</p>
          <div class="client-list">
            <span>Walgreens Pharmacy</span>
            <span>CVS Pharmacy</span>
            <span>Case Jewelers</span>
            <span>Commercial Retail Chains</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-num">02</div>
        <h3>Custom Cabinet & Fixture Fabrication</h3>
        <p>When off-the-shelf doesn't fit — literally or functionally — we fabricate new cabinetry, drawers, and countertops built to exact specification. Commercial-grade, built to last, matched to your existing environment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-num">03</div>
        <h3>Compactor Chute Systems</h3>
        <p>Design, fabrication, and installation of trash compactor chutes that pass through walls — including the gates and access points. Built to code, built to commercial standards, built to last.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-num">04</div>
        <h3>Structural & Technical Fabrication</h3>
        <p>Custom one-of-a-kind fabrication for structural and technical challenges in commercial environments. If it needs to be designed from scratch and built right, we do it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DIFFERENTIATOR -->
  <section class="diff-section">
    <div class="diff-inner reveal">
      <p class="section-label">Why Us</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">The Last Call<br/>That Solves It</h2>
      <div class="diff-cols">
        <div class="diff-col">
          <p>Most facilities managers have a rotation of maintenance vendors they call for standard work. Streich Force Enterprise is not a replacement for that. We're the call you make when:</p>
        </div>
        <div class="diff-col">
          <div class="diff-list">
            <div class="diff-item">
              <span class="diff-icon">→</span>
              <span>Standard repair attempts have failed or been refused</span>
            </div>
            <div class="diff-item">
              <span class="diff-icon">→</span>
              <span>The repair requires fabricating a part that no longer exists</span>
            </div>
            <div class="diff-item">
              <span class="diff-icon">→</span>
              <span>The scope crosses multiple trades or doesn't fit a single category</span>
            </div>
            <div class="diff-item">
              <span class="diff-icon">→</span>
              <span>You need something custom-built to exact commercial specifications</span>
            </div>
            <div class="diff-item">
              <span class="diff-icon">→</span>
              <span>The work needs to be done right the first time, no second guessing</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="cta-banner reveal">
    <div class="cta-text">
      <h3 class="cta-title">Have a Job No One Else Has Been Able to Fix?</h3>
      <p class="cta-sub">Describe what you're dealing with and we'll tell you honestly whether we can solve it.</p>
    </div>
    <a href="mailto:enterprise@streichforce.com" class="btn-primary">Contact Enterprise</a>
  </div>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .division-hero {
    min-height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 0 var(--page-pad) 6rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--iron);
  }

  .hero-grid-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    animation: gridShift 20s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes gridShift {
    from { transform: translateY(0); }
    to { transform: translateY(60px); }
  }

  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.2s;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.4s;
  }

  .hero-title .accent { color: var(--rust); }

  .hero-rule {
    width: 80px; height: 3px;
    background: var(--rust);
    margin: 2rem 0;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.6s;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--mist);
    max-width: 540px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.8s;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 1s;
  }

  /* STATEMENT */
  .statement-section {
    padding: 5rem var(--page-pad);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--iron);
  }

  .statement-inner {
    max-width: 860px;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3vw, 1.9rem);
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--bone);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--rust);
    padding-left: 2rem;
    font-style: normal;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  /* SERVICES */
  .content-section { padding: 7rem var(--page-pad); }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    background: var(--iron);
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    padding: 3rem;
    transition: background 0.3s;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .service-card:hover { background: var(--steel); }

  .service-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--iron);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .service-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--mist);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .clients-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .client-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .client-list span {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--iron);
    color: var(--mist);
  }

  /* DIFFERENTIATOR */
  .diff-section {
    padding: 6rem var(--page-pad);
    background: var(--charcoal);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--iron);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--iron);
  }

  .diff-inner { }

  .diff-cols {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .diff-col p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--mist);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .diff-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .diff-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .diff-icon {
    color: var(--rust);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  .diff-item span:last-child {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--bone);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-banner {
    margin: 6rem var(--page-pad);
    padding: 4rem;
    background: var(--charcoal);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--rust);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 3rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-sub { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--mist); }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .diff-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .cta-banner { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  }
</style>
